<doc id="864574" wikidata="Q7162088" url="?curid=864574" title="Pen Dal-aderyn">
<text>Pen Dal-aderyn is the westernmost point of mainland Wales.

It is in Pembrokeshire, west of St Davids. It means &#x27;Bird-catching Head&#x27; in Welsh.

